title: Drupalgeddon2
extract: Meaning even anonymous users could exploit the vulnerability. CI (Confidentiality impact): All - All non-public data was accessible because of the vulnerability. II (Integrity impact): All - The data could have been easily modified or deleted. E (Exploit) - An exploit is known to exist or is documented.Apr 17, 2018
